OL,3,CCordons in place after gunman opens
OL,4,Cfire on house
OL,6,FA gunman opened fire at a house
OL,7,Fleaving multiple bullet holes in a
OL,8,Ffront window.
OL,10,FPolice were called to School House
OL,11,FRoad in Oldham, Greater Manchester, at
OL,12,Faround 1pm on Sunday 15 February to
OL,13,Freports of criminal damage.
OL,15,FWhen officers arrived, they discovered
OL,16,Fa firearm had been discharged at the
OL,17,Fproperty. No one was injured.
