OL,6,FForensic officers were at the scene
OL,7,Fthis morning on Monday 16 February
OL,8,Fphotographing the damage as enquiries
OL,9,Fcontinued.
OL,11,FA cordon remains in place on School
OL,12,FHouse Road, with several police
OL,13,Fvehicles stationed nearby. A second
OL,14,Fcordon has also been set up on
OL,15,FRoundthorn Road, behind the property
OL,16,Fbelieved to have been targeted.
OL,18,FOfficers are appealing for witnesses
OL,19,Fand for anyone with CCTV or dashcam
OL,20,Ffootage to come forward.
