OL,6,FIn a statement, a GMP spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "At around 1pm yesterday (Sunday
OL,8,F15 February 2026), we were called to
OL,9,Freports of criminal damage at an
OL,10,Faddress on School House Road in
OL,11,FOldham. Officers attended the scene
OL,12,Fand confirmed that there had been a
OL,13,Ffirearms discharge.
OL,15,F"A scene remains in place whilst we
OL,16,Fcontinue our enquiries and thankfully,
OL,17,Fno injuries have been reported.
OL,18,FInvestigations are ongoing.
